<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>JSC UNIT — Special Operations</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Barlow:wght@400;500;600&family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@500;600&display=swap');

:root{
  --bg:#0B0D09;
  --bg-panel:#14170F;
  --line:#2B301F;
  --line-soft:#22261A;
  --accent:#9CB380;
  --accent-dim:#5F7050;
  --amber:#C9A227;
  --danger:#B0392C;
  --text:#E7E7DD;
  --text-muted:#9A9C8E;
  --text-dim:#6B6E5F;
}

*{ margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
html{ scroll-behavior:smooth; }

body{
  background:var(--bg);
  color:var(--text);
  font-family:'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-size:15.5px;
  line-height:1.65;
  position:relative;
  min-height:100vh;
}
body::before{
  content:"";
  position:fixed; inset:0;
  pointer-events:none;
  z-index:0;
  background:repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 0px, rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 3px);
}

a{ color:inherit; text-decoration:none; cursor:pointer; }

h1,h2,h3,h4{
  font-family:'Oswald', sans-serif;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  letter-spacing:0.03em;
  font-weight:600;
  color:var(--text);
}

.mono-tag{
  font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
  letter-spacing:0.18em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  font-size:11.5px;
  color:var(--accent);
}

.classbar{
  background:var(--danger);
  color:#F4E9E7;
  font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
  letter-spacing:0.14em;
  font-size:11px;
  text-align:center;
  padding:5px 8px;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  position:relative;
  z-index:2;
}

header{
  background:var(--bg-panel);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  position:relative;
  z-index:5;
}
.header-inner{
  max-width:1100px;
  margin:0 auto;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:space-between;
  padding:20px 24px 16px;
  gap:16px;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
}
.brand{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; }
.brand-mark{
  width:38px; height:38px;
  border:1.5px solid var(--accent);
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  transform:rotate(45deg);
  flex-shrink:0;
}
.brand-mark span{
  transform:rotate(-45deg);
  font-family:'Oswald', sans-serif;
  font-weight:700;
  font-size:14px;
  color:var(--accent);
}
.brand-text h1{ font-size:22px; letter-spacing:0.08em; line-height:1; }
.brand-text .sub{
  font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
  font-size:11px;
  letter-spacing:0.2em;
  color:var(--text-dim);
  text-transform:uppercase;
  margin-top:3px;
}

.auth-area{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; }
.auth-btn{
  font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
  font-size:12.5px;
  letter-spacing:0.1em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  color:var(--text-muted);
  background:none;
  padding:8px 14px;
  cursor:pointer;
}
.auth-btn:hover{ border-color:var(--accent); color:var(--accent); }
.auth-chip{
  display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
  font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
  font-size:12.5px;
  letter-spacing:0.08em;
  color:var(--amber);
  border:1px solid var(--amber);
  padding:6px 12px;
}
.auth-chip .dot{
  width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--amber);
  flex-shrink:0;
}

nav.mainnav{ border-top:1px solid var(--line-soft); }
.nav-inner{
  max-width:1100px;
  margin:0 auto;
  display:flex;
  padding:0 24px;
  overflow-x:auto;
}
.nav-inner a{
  font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
  font-size:13.5px;
  letter-spacing:0.14em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--text-muted);
  padding:13px 18px 12px;
  border-bottom:2px solid transparent;
  white-space:nowrap;
}
.nav-inner a:hover{ color:var(--text); }
.nav-inner a.active{ color:var(--accent); border-bottom:2px solid var(--accent); }

main{ position:relative; z-index:2; }
.page{ display:none; }
.page.active{ display:block; }

.hero{ max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; padding:70px 24px 50px; }
.hero.compact{ padding-bottom:20px; }
.hero .mono-tag{ display:block; margin-bottom:14px; }
.hero h2{ font-size:clamp(30px, 5vw, 50px); line-height:1.12; max-width:820px; }
.hero h2 em{ font-style:normal; color:var(--accent); }
.hero p.lead{ margin-top:20px; max-width:600px; color:var(--text-muted); font-size:16px; }

.hero-actions{ display:flex; gap:12px; margin-top:30px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
.btn{
  display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
  padding:12px 22px;
  font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
  font-size:14px; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase;
  border:1px solid var(--accent); color:var(--accent);
  clip-path:polygon(10px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 10px), calc(100% - 10px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 10px);
  transition:background .15s, color .15s;
  background:none; cursor:pointer;
}
.btn:hover{ background:var(--accent); color:#0B0D09; }
.btn.solid{ background:var(--accent); color:#0B0D09; }
.btn.solid:hover{ background:var(--text); border-color:var(--text); }

.section{ max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; padding:10px 24px 60px; }
.section.narrow{ max-width:640px; }
.section-head{
  display:flex; align-items:baseline; justify-content:space-between;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); padding-bottom:14px; margin-bottom:28px;
}
.section-head h3{ font-size:24px; }

.grid{ display:grid; gap:18px; }
.grid.cols-3{ grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr); }
.grid.cols-2{ grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr); }

.hud-panel{
  background:var(--bg-panel); border:1px solid var(--line);
  padding:22px 22px 20px; position:relative;
}
.hud-panel::before, .hud-panel::after{
  content:""; position:absolute; width:14px; height:14px;
  border-color:var(--accent); border-style:solid; opacity:0.85;
}
.hud-panel::before{ top:-1px; left:-1px; border-width:1.5px 0 0 1.5px; }
.hud-panel::after{ bottom:-1px; right:-1px; border-width:0 1.5px 1.5px 0; }
.hud-panel h4{ font-size:16px; margin-bottom:10px; color:var(--text); }
.hud-panel p{ color:var(--text-muted); font-size:14.5px; }
.hud-panel .idx{
  font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size:12px;
  color:var(--accent-dim); letter-spacing:0.14em; margin-bottom:8px; display:block;
}
.hud-panel ul.spec-list{ list-style:none; margin-top:10px; }
.hud-panel ul.spec-list li{
  font-size:13.5px; color:var(--text-muted);
  padding:5px 0 5px 14px; position:relative;
}
.hud-panel ul.spec-list li::before{
  content:"—"; position:absolute; left:0; color:var(--accent-dim);
}

/* photo slot for weapon images the user will add */
.photo-slot{
  width:100%; height:140px; margin-bottom:14px;
  border:1px dashed var(--line);
  background:var(--bg);
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  overflow:hidden;
}
.photo-slot img{ width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; display:block; }
.photo-fallback{
  display:none; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:6px;
  color:var(--text-dim); font-size:12px; text-align:center; padding:10px;
}
.photo-fallback code{
  color:var(--accent-dim); font-size:11px;
  font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
}

.roster-card{ background:var(--bg-panel); border:1px solid var(--line); padding:20px; position:relative; cursor:pointer; transition:border-color .15s; }
.roster-card:hover{ border-color:var(--accent-dim); }
.roster-top{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; margin-bottom:14px; }
.roster-avatar{
  width:52px; height:52px; border:1.5px solid var(--accent-dim);
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  font-family:'Oswald', sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:18px;
  color:var(--accent); flex-shrink:0;
}
.roster-tag{
  font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size:10.5px;
  letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--amber);
  border:1px solid var(--amber); padding:3px 8px;
}
.roster-card h4{ font-size:17px; margin-top:2px; }
.roster-role{
  font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size:12.5px;
  letter-spacing:0.08em; color:var(--text-dim); text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;
}
.roster-card p{ color:var(--text-muted); font-size:14px; margin-bottom:12px; }
.roster-weap{
  border-top:1px dashed var(--line); padding-top:10px;
  font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size:12.5px;
  letter-spacing:0.06em; color:var(--text-dim); text-transform:uppercase;
  display:flex; justify-content:space-between;
}
.roster-weap span:last-child{ color:var(--accent); }
.roster-more{
  margin-top:10px; font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
  font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--accent);
}

.roe-list{ list-style:none; }
.roe-list li{ display:flex; gap:14px; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-soft); }
.roe-list li:last-child{ border-bottom:none; }
.roe-num{
  font-family:'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size:13px; color:var(--accent);
  border:1px solid var(--accent-dim); width:26px; height:26px;
  flex-shrink:0; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
}
.roe-list p{ color:var(--text-muted); font-size:14.5px; }
.roe-list strong{ color:var(--text); font-weight:600; }

.contact-field label{
  display:block; font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size:12px;
  letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--text-dim); margin-bottom:7px;
}
.contact-field input, .contact-field textarea{
  width:100%; background:var(--bg); border:1px solid var(--line); color:var(--text);
  padding:11px 12px; font-family:'Barlow', sans-serif; font-size:14px; outline:none;
}
.contact-field input:focus, .contact-field textarea:focus{ border-color:var(--accent); }
.contact-field{ margin-bottom:16px; }
.contact-note{ font-size:13px; color:var(--text-dim); margin-top:6px; min-height:16px; }

/* board */
.board-post{
  border:1px solid var(--line); background:var(--bg-panel);
  padding:16px 18px; margin-bottom:12px;
}
.board-post-top{
  display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:baseline; margin-bottom:6px; gap:10px;
}
.board-post-top h4{ font-size:15px; }
.board-post-meta{
  font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size:11.5px;
  color:var(--text-dim); letter-spacing:0.06em; white-space:nowrap;
}
.board-post p{ color:var(--text-muted); font-size:14px; }
.board-post .del-btn{
  margin-top:10px; font-family:'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size:11.5px;
  letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--danger);
  background:none; border:1px solid var(--danger); padding:4px 10px; cursor:pointer;
}

footer{ border-top:1px solid var(--line); background:var(--bg-panel); position:relative; z-index:2; }
.footer-inner{
  max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; padding:26px 24px;
  display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px;
}
.footer-inner .mono-tag{ color:var(--text-dim); }

@media (max-width:760px){
  .grid.cols-3, .grid.cols-2{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .header-inner{ flex-wrap:wrap; gap:14px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="classbar">Unclassified // For Training &amp; Simulation Use Only</div>

<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="brand">
      <div class="brand-mark"><span>JSC</span></div>
      <div class="brand-text">
        <h1>JSC UNIT</h1>
        <div class="sub">Special Operations Command</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="auth-area" id="authArea"></div>
  </div>
  <nav class="mainnav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a id="nav-homePage" onclick="showPage('homePage')" class="active" data-i18n="nav_home">Home</a>
      <a id="nav-aboutPage" onclick="showPage('aboutPage')" data-i18n="nav_about">About</a>
      <a id="nav-missionPage" onclick="showPage('missionPage')" data-i18n="nav_mission">Mission</a>
      <a id="nav-operationsPage" onclick="showPage('operationsPage')" data-i18n="nav_operations">Operations</a>
      <a id="nav-boardPage" onclick="showPage('boardPage')" data-i18n="nav_board">Board</a>
      <a id="nav-contactPage" onclick="showPage('contactPage')" data-i18n="nav_contact">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </nav>
</header>

<main>

  <!-- ===== HOME ===== -->
  <div class="page active" id="homePage">
    <div class="hero">
      <span class="mono-tag" data-i18n="home_tag">// Precision · Silence · Unity</span>
      <h2 data-i18n-html="home_title">Built for the moment<br>no one else <em>answers the call.</em></h2>
      <p class="lead" data-i18n="home_lead">JSC Unit is a specialist team focused on high-risk rescue and counter-terror operations. We combine tactics, technology, and decisive action to save lives and neutralize threats.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a onclick="showPage('missionPage')" class="btn solid" data-i18n="home_btn_mission">View Mission Profiles</a>
        <a onclick="showPage('aboutPage')" class="btn" data-i18n="home_btn_about">Meet the Unit</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h3 data-i18n="home_cap_head">Core Capabilities</h3>
        <span class="mono-tag">01 — 03</span>
      </div>
      <div class="grid cols-3">
        <div class="hud-panel">
          <span class="idx" data-i18n="cap1_idx">Capability / 01</span>
          <h4 data-i18n="cap1_title">Search &amp; Rescue</h4>
          <p data-i18n="cap1_body">Rapid response teams deploy to locate and extract civilians from disaster zones, hostile environments, or collapsed structures.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hud-panel">
          <span class="idx" data-i18n="cap2_idx">Capability / 02</span>
          <h4 data-i18n="cap2_title">Counter-Terrorism</h4>
          <p data-i18n="cap2_body">Precision raids and containment strategies to neutralize active threats while minimizing collateral impact.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hud-panel">
          <span class="idx" data-i18n="cap3_idx">Capability / 03</span>
          <h4 data-i18n="cap3_title">Hostage Rescue</h4>
          <p data-i18n="cap3_body">High-stakes breaching and close-quarters tactics focused on securing hostages and safe extraction.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h3 data-i18n="home_roster_head">Unit Roster — Preview</h3>
        <a onclick="showPage('aboutPage')" class="mono-tag" data-i18n="home_roster_link">Full Roster →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="grid cols-3">
        <div class="roster-card" onclick="showPage('detailJinoo')">
          <div class="roster-top">
            <div class="roster-avatar">JN</div>
            <div class="roster-tag" data-i18n="tag_lead">Lead</div>
          </div>
          <h4>JINOO</h4>
          <div class="roster-role" data-i18n="role_leader">Team Leader</div>
          <p data-i18n="home_bio_jinoo">Leads strategic planning and command decisions. Known for calm leadership in high-pressure scenarios.</p>
          <div class="roster-more" data-i18n="view_profile">View full profile →</div>
        </div>
        <div class="roster-card" onclick="showPage('detailChris')">
          <div class="roster-top">
            <div class="roster-avatar">CH</div>
            <div class="roster-tag" data-i18n="tag_ops">Ops</div>
          </div>
          <h4>CHRIS</h4>
          <div class="roster-role" data-i18n="role_ops">Operations Chief</div>
          <p data-i18n="home_bio_chris">Coordinates mission logistics and tactical sequencing. Real-time adjustments and comms lead.</p>
          <div class="roster-more" data-i18n="view_profile">View full profile →</div>
        </div>
        <div class="roster-card" onclick="showPage('detailSion')">
          <div class="roster-top">
            <div class="roster-avatar">SI</div>
            <div class="roster-tag" data-i18n="tag_assault">Assault</div>
          </div>
          <h4>SION</h4>
          <div class="roster-role" data-i18n="role_assault">Assault Lead</div>
          <p data-i18n="home_bio_sion">Leads entry teams and breaching operations. Expert in close-quarters dynamic entry.</p>
          <div class="roster-more" data-i18n="view_profile">View full profile →</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== ABOUT ===== -->
  <div class="page" id="aboutPage">
    <div class="hero compact">
      <span class="mono-tag" data-i18n="about_tag">// Unit Profile</span>
      <h2 data-i18n-html="about_title">About the <em>Unit.</em></h2>
      <p class="lead" data-i18n="home_lead">JSC Unit is a specialist team focused on high-risk rescue and counter-terror operations. We combine tactics, technology, and decisive action to save lives and neutralize threats.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-head"><h3 data-i18n="about_roles_head">Primary Roles</h3></div>
      <div class="grid cols-2">
        <div class="hud-panel">
          <span class="idx" data-i18n="roleA_idx">Role Set / A</span>
          <h4 data-i18n="roleA_title">Rescue &amp; Extraction</h4>
          <p data-i18n="roleA_body">The unit specializes in search and rescue, trained for rapid insertion, precision breaching, and coordinated extraction under duress.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hud-panel">
          <span class="idx" data-i18n="roleB_idx">Role Set / B</span>
          <h4 data-i18n="roleB_title">Counter-Terror &amp; Hostage Recovery</h4>
          <p data-i18n="roleB_body">Operators train continuously for counter-terrorism and hostage rescue missions, prioritizing speed, precision, and civilian safety.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h3 data-i18n="about_weap_head">Standard Issue Weapons</h3>
        <span class="mono-tag" data-i18n="about_weap_tag">Reference Only</span>
      </div>
      <p class="contact-note" style="margin-bottom:18px;" data-i18n="photo_hint">Drop your own weapon photos into an "images" folder next to this file, using the filenames below — they will appear automatically.</p>
      <div class="grid cols-3">
        <div class="hud-panel">
          <div class="photo-slot">
            <img src="images/ak47.jpg" alt="AK-47" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';">
            <div class="photo-fallback"><span data-i18n="photo_placeholder">Add a photo here</span><br><code>images/ak47.jpg</code></div>
          </div>
          <span class="idx" data-i18n="weap1_idx">Standard / 01</span>
          <h4>AK-47</h4>
          <p data-i18n="weap1_body">Reliable, rugged battle rifle used by lead operators for robust performance across diverse environments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hud-panel">
          <div class="photo-slot">
            <img src="images/urgi.jpg" alt="URG-I" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';">
            <div class="photo-fallback"><span data-i18n="photo_placeholder">Add a photo here</span><br><code>images/urgi.jpg</code></div>
          </div>
          <span class="idx" data-i18n="weap2_idx">Standard / 02</span>
          <h4>URG-I</h4>
          <p data-i18n="weap2_body">Compact carbine favored for close-quarters engagement and rapid maneuvering inside confined structures.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hud-panel">
          <div class="photo-slot">
            <img src="images/m4a1.jpg" alt="M4A1 SOPMOD II" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';">
            <div class="photo-fallback"><span data-i18n="photo_placeholder">Add a photo here</span><br><code>images/m4a1.jpg</code></div>
          </div>
          <span class="idx" data-i18n="weap3_idx">Standard / 03</span>
          <h4>M4A1 SOPMOD II</h4>
          <p data-i18n="weap3_body">Modular rifle platform with SOPMOD upgrades, optimized for modern special operations profiles.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h3 data-i18n="about_team_head">Team Members</h3>
        <span class="mono-tag" data-i18n="about_team_tag">3 Operators Listed</span>
      </div>
      <div class="grid cols-3">
        <div class="roster-card" onclick="showPage('detailJinoo')">
          <div class="roster-top">
            <div class="roster-avatar">JN</div>
            <div class="roster-tag" data-i18n="tag_lead">Lead</div>
          </div>
          <h4>JINOO</h4>
          <div class="roster-role" data-i18n="role_leader">Team Leader</div>
          <p data-i18n="about_bio_jinoo">Leads strategic planning and command decisions. Oversees mission planning, risk assessment, and end-state accountability. Known for calm leadership in high-pressure rescue and assault scenarios.</p>
          <div class="roster-weap"><span data-i18n="primary_weapon">Primary Weapon</span><span>AK-47</span></div>
          <div class="roster-more" data-i18n="view_profile">View full profile →</div>
        </div>
        <div class="roster-card" onclick="showPage('detailChris')">
          <div class="roster-top">
            <div class="roster-avatar">CH</div>
            <div class="roster-tag" data-i18n="tag_ops">Ops</div>
          </div>
