        <div class="hud-panel">
          <span class="idx" data-i18n="profile3_idx">Profile / 03</span>
          <h4 data-i18n="cap3_title">Hostage Rescue</h4>
          <p data-i18n="profile3_body">High-stakes breaching and close-quarters tactics focused on securing hostages, safe extraction, and suspect containment. Dynamic entry planning and real-time negotiation support are core capabilities.</p>
        </div>
